<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>端午安康 · 粽叶飘香</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        body {
            background: #1c402e;
            font-family: "Microsoft Yahei", sans-serif;
            color: #fff;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }
        /* 粽叶飘落动画 */
        .leaf {
            position: fixed;
            width: 35px;
            height: 60px;
            background:#508c47;
            border-radius: 0 100%;
            opacity: 0.7;
            animation: fall 10s linear infinite;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        @keyframes fall {
            0%{transform: translateY(-80px) rotate(0deg);opacity:0.8;}
            100%{transform: translateY(110vh) rotate(360deg);opacity:0;}
        }
        .container{
            position: relative;
            z-index:2;
            max-width:900px;
            margin:0 auto;
            padding:60px 20px;
            text-align:center;
        }
        h1{
            font-size:48px;
            color:#ffdd70;
            margin-bottom:20px;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 8px #00000050;
        }
        .sub-title{
            font-size:20px;
            color:#e8e8e8;
            margin-bottom:40px;
        }
        .card{
            background:rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
            backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
            border-radius:20px;
            padding:35px;
            line-height:2;
            font-size:17px;
        }
        .item-box{
            display:flex;
            flex-wrap:wrap;
            gap:16px;
            justify-content:center;
            margin-top:30px;
        }
        .item{
            background:rgba(255,221,112,0.15);
            padding:12px 22px;
            border-radius:30px;
            border:1px solid #ffdd7060;
        }
        .footer{
            margin-top:50px;
            font-size:14px;
            opacity:0.7;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<!-- 飘落粽叶 -->
<div class="leaf" style="left:8%;animation-delay:0s;"></div>
<div class="leaf" style="left:22%;animation-delay:2s;"></div>
<div class="leaf" style="left:40%;animation-delay:4s;"></div>
<div class="leaf" style="left:65%;animation-delay:1.5s;"></div>
<div class="leaf" style="left:85%;animation-delay:3s;"></div>

<div class="container">
    <h1>🐉 端午安康 🐉</h1>
    <p class="sub-title">岁岁安康 · 粽叶飘香 · 岁岁绵长</p>
    <div class="card">
        <p>
            又是一年端午至，艾草青青，粽叶飘香。
        </p>
        <p>
            吃粽子，挂艾草，系五彩绳，赛龙舟。
            承载千年的民俗，寄托平安顺遂的美好祝愿。
        </p>
        <p style="margin-top:15px;">愿清风常伴，喜乐无忧，岁岁平安，万事安康！</p>
        <div class="item-box">
            <div class="item">🥟 食粽子</div>
            <div class="item">🎋 挂艾草</div>
            <div class="item">🎗️ 五彩绳</div>
            <div class="item">🚣 赛龙舟</div>
            <div class="item>🍵 饮雄黄</div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
        祝大家端午安康，阖家幸福
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>

